msgstr "Do not use GPTQ/AWQ models with FSDP+QLoRA"

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:711
msgid "您可以通过 `accelerate config` 根据提示回答一系列问题后，生成 多机 FSDP 所需的配置文件。"
msgstr "You can use `accelerate config` to answer a series of questions and generate the configuration file required for multi-node FSDP."

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:713
msgid "当然您也可以根据需求自行配置 fsdp_config.yaml 。"
msgstr "Of course, you can also configure fsdp_config.yaml yourself according to your needs."

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:746
msgid "这份yaml文件里，您主要需要注意配置的参数是以下四个："
msgstr "In this YAML file, the key parameters you need to configure are the following four:"

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:748
msgid "num_machines: 节点（机器）的数量。"
msgstr "num_machines: Number of nodes (machines)."

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:749
msgid "num_processes: 所有节点上的 GPU 总数，即 num_machines * num_processes_per_machine。"
msgstr "num_processes: Total number of GPUs across all nodes, i.e., num_machines * num_processes_per_machine."

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:750
msgid "main_process_ip: 主进程所在节点的 IP 地址；请确保所有节点使用相同的 IP。"
msgstr "main_process_ip: IP address of the node where the main process runs; ensure all nodes use the same IP."

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:751
msgid "main_process_port: 主进程的端口号；请确保所有节点使用相同的端口。"
msgstr "main_process_port: Port of the main process; ensure all nodes use the same port."

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:752
msgid "machine_rank: 当前节点（机器）的编号，从 0 开始；并且主节点（main_process_ip）的 machine_rank 必须为 0。"
msgstr "machine_rank: Index of the current node (machine), starting from 0; the main node (main_process_ip) must have machine_rank 0."

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:754
msgid "当配置完成后，在所有机器上运行如下命令即可启动FSDP的多机多卡训练："
msgstr "After the configuration is complete, run the following command on all machines to start multi-node multi-card FSDP training:"

#: ../../source/advanced/distributed.rst:18
msgid "`FSDP2 <https://pytorch.org/tutorials/intermediate/FSDP_tutorial.html>`__ 在集成FSDP1基础功能的前提下，摒弃了 FSDP1 将参数压扁拼接的做法，转而基于 DTensor 实现逐参数切分，这一架构升级在完整保留模型原始结构的同时，显著提升了计算与通信的重叠效率，进而增强训练性能。"
msgstr "`FSDP2 <https://pytorch.org/tutorials/intermediate/FSDP_tutorial.html>`__, while integrating the basic functionality of FSDP1, abandons FSDP1's approach of flattening and concatenating parameters and instead implements per-parameter sharding based on DTensor. This architectural upgrade, while fully preserving the original model structure, significantly improves the overlap efficiency of computation and communication, thereby enhancing training performance."

